### GET /api/v1/trips/{id}
### Descripción: Obtener un viaje por id. Requiere JWT (acceso según rol/ABAC).
### Headers requeridos: Authorization: Bearer <token>
### Códigos: 200 OK (TripDto) | 403 | 404 TRIP_NOT_FOUND | 400

# @name getTrip
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/trips/{{TRIP_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{ACCESS_TOKEN}}

### Response esperado (200):
# {
#   "id", "status", "pickupAddress", "dropoffAddress", "estimatedAmount", "finalAmount", "currency", "createdAtUtc"
# }

### Response error (404): { "error", "code": "TRIP_NOT_FOUND" }
### Response error (403): Forbidden
